text: The Crinn is an American mathcore band from St. Paul, Minnesota, United States, formed in 2005. On April 20, 2010, they released their debut album Dreaming Saturn through Nuclear Blast records. ==Discography== * Kills Curiosity (EP) (Self Released, 2006) * Self Titled (EP) (Corrosive, 2007) * Dreaming Saturn (Nuclear Blast, 2010) * Shadowbreather (Self-released, 2015) ==References== ==External links== *** Category:Musical groups from Minnesota Category:Musical groups established in 2005 Category:Mathcore musical groups Category:Nuclear Blast artists
title: The Crinn
